title: General Chakravarthi
subTitle: Chakravarthi's daughter Rani falls in love with Saker and gets pregnant with his child. Later, her mother decides to keep it a secret, but things become complicated when Saker is reported to be dead.

title: Idhu Namma Bhoomi
subTitle: Gopi loves Nalini, but her father, Rathnavel, opposes their marriage due to an old feud with Gopi's father, Jaganathan. Determined to bring peace, Gopi resolves to reunite the two estranged families.

title: Kanda Naal Mudhal
subTitle: After quarrelling as children, two young adults discover their path to love.

title: Veera Padhakkam
subTitle: A corrupt, ambitious policeman is forced to mend his ways after witnessing the consequences of his role in a relative's life.

title: Kasi
subTitle: Having endured years of blindness and the hardships that accompanied it, a visually impaired musician is tricked into believing that a physician can restore his sight.

title: Subash
subTitle: Subash, an unemployed young man, joins the army to be able to marry his lover. However, when he returns from his deployment, he is shocked to see his brother leading a corrupt life.

title: Gopura Vasalile
subTitle: After losing his lover, teacher Manohar's life stagnates. His friends intervene, reigniting his passion for life and opening doors to new love.

title: Nilaave Vaa
subTitle: Siluvai, a Christian man, wants to get married to Sangeetha, a Hindu woman who is already engaged to Siva. Her father is against their union, but Siva decides to help them.
